title: Vulcan launch demonstrates new solid rocket boosters
summary: The first launch of United Launch Alliance’s Vulcan Centaur was also a successful demonstration of new solid rocket boosters developed by Northrop Grumman for the vehicle.

title: Airbus and Voyager finalize Starlab joint venture
summary: Voyager Space and Airbus Defence and Space have finalized a partnership to develop the Starlab commercial space station, seeking to win customers for it from both sides of the Atlantic.
